Title: Object: Essai de procédé de gravure à la plume: La fuite en Égypte
Description: The Flight into Egypt; an angel appearing to the Virgin, on donkey, and Joseph, at left approaching sea. c.1860s? Etching, with some surface tone
Bibliographic references: Beraldi 1885-92 / Les Graveurs du dix-neuvième siècle (171)
